{"tid":2274370,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"（黃色經濟圈）報紙檔睇到野狼與瑪利，呢套經典竟然出左續集，即掃","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T11:16:36.000Z","uid":43785,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"30056fcd349862ff400ea31f00d7906313d2a23c","tid":2274370,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"今日行過報紙檔，睇到和仔出咗新一套野狼與瑪莉2，即刻掃左番來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwUiW96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwUiW96.jpg&h=0822e362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內容易唔講啦，總之就痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係黃圈，但唔係個個都知呢套野<br />\n我都介紹下先，<br />\n當年第一集出左唔少經典圖，好似呢張咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾人廣傳緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPfYW9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPfYW9f.jpg&h=15b08a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想睇番既，漫畫人等漫畫網站都有齊晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一集仲紅到拍埋電影<br />\n<br />\n當中最經典一幕，當然就係連詩雅半裸上身食台灣土產大鵰燒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hQ6mDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hQ6mDa.jpg&h=d8e9eccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n更因此殿定樂壇公廁地位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢篇唔長好快就完，你地買左第一期未呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwUiW96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwUiW96.jpg&h=0822e362&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ff5e43d078f6cd4a076b46493986d4e08ac1df5","tid":2274370,"uid":605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"你點睇的"},{"pid":"f3e9d2a179914d63907f4d122783c2a5fb89a83c","tid":2274370,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir"},{"pid":"2290ea0338f7cb89fdb1b4bb6c68c5e171860b44","tid":2274370,"uid":305696,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:33:26.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"607f426da751a1a6